description: The index is a rules-based, equal-weighted index that tracks the performance of the top 100 U.S.-listed ETFs. The sub-adviser has adopted a policy to invest, under normal circumstances, at least 80% of the fund's net assets, plus the amount of any borrowings for investment purposes, in the ETFs that comprise the index.
name: DriveWealth ETF Trust - DriveWealth ICE 100 Index ETF
